{#
name: Summary Generator
description: Generate summaries from content source with configurable length and format
tags: [report, summary, llm]
parameters:
  - name: skill_name
    type: str
    description: Skill display name
    required: true
  - name: skill_description
    type: str
    description: Brief description of summary generation purpose
    required: true
  - name: content_source
    type: str
    description: Source of content to summarize (e.g. documents, api, stream)
    required: true
  - name: summary_length
    type: str
    description: Target length (e.g. short, medium, long)
    default: "medium"
  - name: format
    type: str
    description: Output format (e.g. plain, markdown, bullet_points)
    default: "markdown"
examples:
  - "Summarize meeting notes into bullet points"
  - "Generate executive summary from long documents"
#}
---
name: {{ skill_name | kebab_case }}
description: {{ skill_description }}
metadata:
  author: owlclaw
  version: "1.0"
owlclaw:
  spec_version: "1.0"
  task_type: report
---
# {{ skill_name }} — 使用指南

## 目标

{{ skill_description }}

## 配置

- 内容源：{{ content_source }}
- 摘要长度：{{ summary_length }}
- 输出格式：{{ format }}

## 生成逻辑

1. 从 content_source 获取原始内容
2. 按 summary_length 控制输出篇幅
3. 生成摘要并格式化为 format 指定形式
4. 返回或持久化结果

## 注意事项

- summary_length 建议：short（<200 字）、medium（~500 字）、long（~1000 字）
- format 为 bullet_points 时输出要点列表
- 超长内容建议先分块再汇总
